<span class="postbody">Umm, hate to burst your bubble, but you asked for it...
<br />

<br />
First, Romar's is Elemental gear.  Aside from the robe and legs, you will not see 1 piece drop in Time, if you want us to get technical.  Not to mention, you do not want anyone to get started on how rare a Time robe seems to drop...
<br />

<br />
Second, unless you can have *two primary only* items equipped at the same time, you cannot count the Int from both the epic and the Wand of Temporal Power.
<br />

<br />
Lastly, well, if you ever see someone decked out in full Romar's with just a Tobrin's eyepatch, take a picture.  That freak show belongs on Jerry Springer...</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
</td></tr>
